<strong>REFERENCE LIST ENTRY</strong>
<br>
<br>
Add a reference list at the end of your essay citing all sources used in the body of your writing.
<br>
<br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	Authors. (Year of publication). Title of article. <em>Name of Publication, volume</em>(issue), 
	page numbers. doi:Digital Object Identifier (if assigned)
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	<span class="hover" title="Authors">Smith, A., &amp; Brown, B.</span> 
	(<span class="hover" title="Year of publication">2056</span>). 
	<span class="hover" title="Title of article">A battle from the beginning: The life and times of a heavyweight champion</span>. 
	<em><span class="hover" title="Name of Publication">Sport and Fitness</span>, 
	<span class="hover" title="volume">14</span></em>(<span class="hover" title="issue">2</span>), 
	<span class="hover" title="page numbers">25&#45;37</span>. 
	doi:<span class="hover" title="Digital Object Identifier">12:3456789012</span>
</blockquote>
